                Setup:
                1. Disable file manager's automount to prevent interference (if applicable)
                2. $ cp /usr/local/share/usb-automount/usb-automount.conf ~/.config/
                3. Edit ~/.config/usb-automount.conf (set your gui file manager)
                4. Start the daemon: $ usb-automount &

                To remove a mounted device (menu will be presented if there is >1):
                $ usb-unmount [eject]
